PrecisAppointment of GORDON D. HAMILTON, of Warman, Saskatchewan, as a Vice-Chairperson of the Canada Industrial Relations Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; and order that GORDON D. HAMILTON be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act, effective March 1, 1999.
